            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                                        <h1 class="headline" itemprop="headline"><a href="/nascar-news/4610893-tony-stewart-investigation-grand-jury-criminal-charges-kevin-ward-death-accident-district-attorney" title="NASCAR drivers curious about Tony Stewart case going to grand jury">NASCAR drivers curious about Tony Stewart case going to grand jury</a> </h1>
                    <span class="sr-only" itemprop="dateModified">September 19, 2014 1:35pm EDT</span>
                    <span class="sr-only" itemprop="datePublished">September 19, 2014 1:32pm EDT</span>
                    <span class="sr-only" itemprop="keywords"></span>
                    <span class="sr-only" itemprop="description">NASCAR drivers and Tony Stewart supporters are curious why a New York district attorney is taking Stewart&#39;s case to a grand jury.</span>
                </div>
            </div>

                            <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-12">
                            <div class="top-media">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="pull-left">
                <div class="sport-tag hidden-xs">
                    <a href="/nascar">NASCAR</a>
                </div>
            </div>
